          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Terms & Conditions: Children between 1-4 years old ride free Student means with any valid student card to be present. KL Hop on Hop off is day tour pass ticket for usage from 9am until 6pm with 24hr validity. (Last pickup at any designated stop at 4pm) Company may change (if any) the term or price if there is any changes on management decision along the offer period."
